ontributions. Alternatively, the poor\nagreement might indicate additional variation in the detailed shape of the IMF,\nbeyond what can currently be inferred from the spectroscopic features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Mar 2014 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Jun 2014 09:38:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
