eded, to include further refinements such as the space-charge evolution of\nthe electron beam, magnetic fields generated by the electron current, and\nlongitudinal proton dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Mar 2014 14:39:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-26"}
